						CLOs
						
						




The Napier Park platform provides investment capabilities across the full spectrum of loan and CLO management / investing. Napier Park currently manages ~$3bn across eight CLO vehicles and has managed another $4bn in previous leveraged loan vehicles. Funds managed by Napier Park have included CLOs, TRS facilities, managed accounts and other structured vehicles. The investment philosophy focuses on capital preservation, a conservative risk profile, active portfolio management, and a diversified portfolio.



