Capital Markets

Company Overview of Napier Park Global Capital (US) LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Napier Park Global Capital (US) LP is an employee owned hedge fund manager. It primarily provides its services to institutional investors, registered funds, funds of funds, pension plans, state and municipal government entities and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, private equity, and alternative investment markets across the globe. The firm’s equity investments are in event driven securities. For fixed income it invests in corporate credit securities, leveraged loan, high-yield credit of European companies, distressed debt and US municipal bond market. The firm invests in mortgage-backed securities...
Napier Park Global Capital (US) LP is an employee owned hedge fund manager. It primarily provides its services to institutional investors, registered funds, funds of funds, pension plans, state and municipal government entities and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, private equity, and alternative investment markets across the globe. The firm’s equity investments are in event driven securities. For fixed income it invests in corporate credit securities, leveraged loan, high-yield credit of European companies, distressed debt and US municipal bond market. The firm invests in mortgage-backed securities using top-down and bottom-up investment approach. For investment in currency market the firm employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with top-down investment approach to create its portfolio. For private equity investments, it invests in growth capital, secondary sales, and recapitalization. In this segment, it typically invests $5 million to $25 million in both majority and significant minority equity positions. The firm also invests in Infrastructure sector in India. Napier Park Global Capital (US) LP is based in New York City with additional offices in London, United Kingdom, and Pfaffikon, Switzerland.
Detailed Description


280 Park Avenue3rd FloorNew York, NY 10017United StatesFounded in 2012



Phone: 212-235-0700

Fax: 212-235-0930

www.napierparkglobal.com/







